                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">The game features classic Monopoly-style gameplay with the added twist of geography-based questions integrated into the experience. Players answer geography questions when purchasing properties, providing an educational dimension to the fun.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 px-5 mx-auto order-1 lg:order-2"><img src="~/css/monopolytraditional.jpg" alt="" class="w-full mb-4 lg:mb-0"></div>
        </div>
